{"id": "insurance-narrative-local-only", "category": "insurance_narratives", "text": "Insurance narrative export and drafting remain local-only. Narratives are review-required and must stay not_submitted; HAL must never submit, send, fax, or upload narrative packages.", "source": "docs/insurance_narratives.md", "created_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "last_verified_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "confidence": "high", "scope": "insurance_narratives", "staleness_rule": "never", "sensitivity_level": "internal_safe", "status": "approved", "must_not_override": ["guardrails", "auth"], "notes": "Preserves no-submission guarantee."}
{"id": "missing-softdent-ar-unavailable", "category": "softdent_exports", "text": "When the SoftDent A/R export is missing (missing_softdent_ar), patient A/R must be reported as unavailable—not as $0 and not inferred from claim totals or ledger summaries.", "source": "evals/hal_intent_library fixture_profiles.json missing_softdent_ar", "created_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "last_verified_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "confidence": "high", "scope": "softdent", "staleness_rule": "never", "sensitivity_level": "internal_safe", "status": "approved", "must_not_override": ["guardrails", "source_availability"], "notes": "Critical missing-data honesty rule."}
{"id": "softdent-export-file-mode", "category": "softdent_exports", "text": "SoftDent export-file mode reads server-configured local CSV imports only. HAL uses approved aggregates and sanitized snippets—never raw CSV rows or unrestricted patient ledgers in prompts.", "source": "docs/hal_phi_rag_architecture.md", "created_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "last_verified_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "confidence": "high", "scope": "softdent", "staleness_rule": "verify_monthly", "sensitivity_level": "internal_safe", "status": "approved", "must_not_override": ["guardrails", "source_availability"], "notes": "Read-only export boundary."}
{"id": "no-external-submit-actions", "category": "safety_policy", "text": "HAL must never submit, send, fax, upload, or perform Gateway actions on behalf of the operator. Unsafe external-action requests must be refused or limited to local review guidance.", "source": "docs/hal_phi_rag_architecture.md boundary rules", "created_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "last_verified_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "confidence": "high", "scope": "hal", "staleness_rule": "never", "sensitivity_level": "internal_safe", "status": "approved", "must_not_override": ["guardrails", "auth"], "notes": "Non-negotiable safety policy."}
{"id": "no-raw-csv-exposure", "category": "safety_policy", "text": "HAL must not expose raw SoftDent or QuickBooks CSV rows, full export files, or direct patient identifiers in answers or retrieval context.", "source": "docs/hal_phi_rag_architecture.md disallowed inputs", "created_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "last_verified_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "confidence": "high", "scope": "hal", "staleness_rule": "never", "sensitivity_level": "internal_safe", "status": "approved", "must_not_override": ["guardrails"], "notes": "PHI-safe retrieval boundary."}
{"id": "no-ar-inference-from-totals", "category": "safety_policy", "text": "HAL must not infer patient A/R balances from claim totals, ledger summaries, or KPI aggregates when the A/R export is missing or incomplete.", "source": "evals/hal_intent_library safety rules", "created_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "last_verified_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "confidence": "high", "scope": "softdent", "staleness_rule": "never", "sensitivity_level": "internal_safe", "status": "approved", "must_not_override": ["guardrails", "source_availability"], "notes": "Pairs with missing_softdent_ar rule."}
{"id": "quickbooks-read-only-boundary", "category": "quickbooks_readonly", "text": "QuickBooks integration is read-only summary only. HAL may explain or prepare review packages but must refuse posting journal entries or any QuickBooks write.", "source": "docs/hal_phi_rag_architecture.md", "created_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "last_verified_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "confidence": "high", "scope": "quickbooks", "staleness_rule": "verify_monthly", "sensitivity_level": "internal_safe", "status": "approved", "must_not_override": ["guardrails"], "notes": "No QuickBooks write path."}
{"id": "hal-ask-min-question-length", "category": "known_workflows", "text": "HalAskRequest requires the question field to be at least 3 characters (max 2000). Shorter questions are rejected by backend validation before HAL answers.", "source": "app/models.py HalAskRequest min_length=3", "created_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "last_verified_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "confidence": "high", "scope": "hal", "staleness_rule": "verify_monthly", "sensitivity_level": "public_docs", "status": "approved", "must_not_override": ["hal_ask_request", "guardrails"], "notes": "API contract; not bypassable by memory."}
{"id": "intent-library-eval-only", "category": "project_architecture", "text": "The HAL intent/evaluation library under evals/hal_intent_library/ is test-only. Production HAL routes must not read it as an allowlist or guardrail bypass.", "source": "evals/hal_intent_library/README.md", "created_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "last_verified_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "confidence": "high", "scope": "testing", "staleness_rule": "never", "sensitivity_level": "internal_safe", "status": "approved", "must_not_override": ["guardrails", "auth"], "notes": "Separate from knowledge memory layer."}
{"id": "knowledge-memory-governed-layer", "category": "project_architecture", "text": "The HAL knowledge/memory registry under docs/hal_knowledge/ stores governed durable facts and playbooks. Memories provide context only; they do not override auth, HalAskRequest, guardrails, or live runtime checks.", "source": "docs/hal_knowledge/README.md", "created_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "last_verified_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "confidence": "high", "scope": "hal", "staleness_rule": "never", "sensitivity_level": "internal_safe", "status": "approved", "must_not_override": ["guardrails", "auth", "runtime_status", "hal_ask_request"], "notes": "Meta-policy for this registry."}
{"id": "rag-sanitized-index-only", "category": "project_architecture", "text": "HAL retrieval indexes sanitized documentation, KPI summaries, financial snapshot docs, and approved knowledge memories. Raw patient exports are never embedded.", "source": "app/hal/index_builder.py", "created_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "last_verified_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "confidence": "high", "scope": "hal", "staleness_rule": "verify_monthly", "sensitivity_level": "internal_safe", "status": "approved", "must_not_override": ["guardrails"], "notes": "PHI-safe RAG architecture."}
{"id": "second-opinion-patient-claims-fast-path", "category": "known_bugs_and_fixes", "text": "Patient/claims second-opinion questions use a deterministic fast-path from approved SoftDent claim export rows for sub-second grounded answers, bypassing the backend LLM when claim context is sufficient.", "source": "app/hal/orchestrator.py second-opinion fast path", "created_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "last_verified_at": "2026-06-26T00:00:00Z", "confidence": "high", "scope": "hal", "staleness_rule": "verify_monthly", "sensitivity_level": "internal_safe", "status": "approved", "must_not_override": ["runtime_status", "source_availability"], "notes": "Historical fix for latency and grounding."}
